@node M041200 "Zone Optimizer"
 Optimize Zones
 --------------

 The game (and the editor) stores zones in a list of structures, when  you've
 worked  for  some  time  on  a  level  and  removed several zones, then this
 structure can get quite messy and filled with holes. This option  runs  down
 the  structures  and  removes  empty  ones.  This causes a faster and better
 working level.

 When ?
 ------
 You should use this option before generating your level ('make'), the reason
 that  I  havn't  included  this  in  'make'  is that this option is not 100%
 tested, so you'll have to call it manualy..

 NOTES:
 ------
 - You should save your work before trying this, the procedure  is  not  100%
   tested yet, and might fail or ruin your level..

@endnode

